Package: ciftier
Type: Package
Title: Read and Write CIFTI-2 Neuroimaging Files
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(c("Bradley", "R"), "Buchsbaum", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
           email = "brad.buchsbaum@gmail.com"))
Description: Pure R implementation of CIFTI-2 format I/O for grayordinate
    neuroimaging data. Reads and writes dense timeseries (.dtseries.nii),
    dense scalars (.dscalar.nii), and dense labels (.dlabel.nii) files
    without requiring external tools such as Connectome Workbench. Provides
    S4 classes mirroring the CIFTI-2 XML schema, user-friendly axis
    abstractions, and optional integration with 'neuroim2' and 'neurosurf'
    for spatially-aware brain imaging objects.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
